200
00:08:54,336 --> 00:08:56,296
No, it can be Italian, just sensible Italian.

201
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:58,080
All right, well, good.

202
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,703
I'm glad we had this settled.

203
00:08:59,794 --> 00:09:03,399
Good. Well, maybe I'll see you at the graduation, maybe I won't.

204
00:09:03,547 --> 00:09:05,502
- What? 
- See you there. Bye.

205
00:09:06,022 --> 00:09:07,205
- Goodbye. 
- Bye.

206
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:15,923
Hey, you and your Armani posse want something to drink, John?

207
00:09:16,021 --> 00:09:17,470
No, no, Lorelai. We're fine, thanks.

208
00:09:18,262 --> 00:09:21,003
So, I've been lying to people about you all day.

209
00:09:21,182 --> 00:09:21,964
About what?

210
00:09:22,129 --> 00:09:25,810
Oh, about how it's not a big deal that you're walking around

211
00:09:25,954 --> 00:09:27,961
with a concerned look on your face with a group of men

212
00:09:28,011 --> 00:09:29,497
with concerned looks on their faces.

213
00:09:30,593 --> 00:09:32,558
I think I've been lying to me a little, too.

214
00:09:32,703 --> 00:09:34,125
We have to close off three more rooms.

215
00:09:34,228 --> 00:09:35,042
Three rooms?

216
00:09:35,625 --> 00:09:37,033
That'll leave us with two.

217
00:09:37,167 --> 00:09:40,162
And, the estimate for the repairs to get everything back

218
00:09:40,218 --> 00:09:42,103
to the quality we had and up to code...

219
00:09:42,881 --> 00:09:44,647
- it's not pretty. 
- No, that's not pretty.

220
00:09:44,833 --> 00:09:46,711
- Mom's leaning toward selling. 
- Selling.

221
00:09:47,249 --> 00:09:49,973
- Nothing's final yet. 
- Yeah, nothing's final.

222
00:09:50,054 --> 00:09:52,738
I just... Rory grew up here.

223
00:09:53,906 --> 00:09:54,853
I grew up here.

224
00:09:55,529 --> 00:09:57,873
Yeah, I better get back to my group.

225
00:09:58,006 --> 00:09:59,178
Right, sure, you go.

226
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:01,130
Hey, be careful not to trip over our guest.

227
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,277
I won't.

228
00:10:07,004 --> 00:10:09,043
Sookie, Jackson, you better not be in bed.

229
00:10:09,526 --> 00:10:10,811
- Are you expecting Lorelai? 
- No.

230
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:13,612
Come on. The night is young and the champagne's cold.

