234
00:10:19,362 --> 00:10:21,988
Sookie, get some glasses, and Jackson, put some music on.

235
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,980
Whatever you want, just make it festive.

236
00:10:24,235 --> 00:10:26,386
- Got it. 
- I don't know what this is, but it's fun.

237
00:10:27,082 --> 00:10:29,606
Let's see. I've got Creedence Clearwater Revival.

238
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:30,975
Good energy, too hillbilly.

239
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:33,743
How you coming with those glasses, Sook?

240
00:10:33,822 --> 00:10:35,260
Just wiping off the fancy ones.

241
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:38,004
Huey Lewis and the News? It's Sookie's.

242
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:40,222
Hey, we all have our guilty pleasures.

243
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:43,893
- Herb Albert and the Tijuana Brass? 
